                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2920" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0383</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8805 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">后谷咖啡：回甜的后谷咖啡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hogood Tastes Sweet</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杜靖川，赵德森，陈伟，姚建文，孔莉，陶小龙，谢云龙</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">后谷咖啡</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">23 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">股权之争；债务危机；后谷咖啡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">无</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013年8月27日，在联合国日内瓦办事处万国宫，来自中国云南的后谷咖啡代表中国在瑞士日内瓦万国宫“感知中国、美丽云南”的文化周上惊艳亮相，引来各国驻日内瓦官员的纷纷围观和品尝。后谷咖啡董事长熊相人在活动上向世界各国驻联合国日内瓦办事处官员和各国驻日内瓦媒体展示并赠送了限量版“后谷熊猫”作为国礼。熊相人表示后谷咖啡有机会香飘万国宫，这是中国咖啡的骄傲，是云南咖啡的骄傲。然而，此时的后谷咖啡刚刚经历了“股权之争”和“债务危机”的沉重打击。本案例将以熊相人所掌管的企业“中国本土第一咖啡” ——后谷咖啡为主线，回顾后谷咖啡2012年“股权之争”和“债务危机”的始末，并了解面对危机熊相人是如何巧妙化解，从而引发读者对风投之争以及云南咖啡未来发展的思考，对其他民族品牌发展具有一定的借鉴和参考价值。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">On August 27, 2013, Hogood representatives from Yunnan(a province of China) debuted amazingly in Palace of Nations, Geneva, Sweden for culture week in “China perception and beautiful Yunnan” on behalf of China, attracting officials of various countries in Geneva to observe and taste. The president of Hogood Xiong Xiangren displayed and gifted the limited “Hogood Panda” to officials in United Nations Office at Geneva and media of various countries in Geneva. Xiong Xiangren showed that Hogood has a chance to be widely spread to Palace of Nations. This is the pride of Chinese coffee and pride of Yunnan coffee. However, Hogood just experienced the heavy impact of “shareholding fighting” and “debt crisis”. The case is based on the “first local coffee”—Hogood mastered by Xiong Xiangren to review the beginning and end of “shareholding fighting” and “debt crisis”  of Hogood in 2012, how to skillfully defuse crisis by Xiong Xiangren, so as to trigger readers’ reflection on risk investment fighting and future development of Yunnan coffee and provide some reference value for other ethnic brand development. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创业管理》、《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">私募股权融资</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
